Anthill Networks SDE Intern Tasks
Task 1: Second-hand Car Buying Application
Objective
Develop a web-based application to facilitate the buying and selling of second-hand cars.
Technology Stack
Frontend: React (Knowledge of Redux and TypeScript is an added advantage)
Database: Firebase or Supabase (alternatives are permissible)
Backend: No backend development required
Features and Roles
Common Features
Authentication: Integration with Google Auth
Admin Role
Car Management: Ability to add, update car details, and update pricing.
Listing and Requests: View listings and manage purchase requests from users.
User Role
Car Search and Request: Users can search for cars and request to purchase them.
Design Constraints
Pages Required: A minimum of three pages; additional pages from the provided Figma design can be ignored.
You are expected to create a responsive web version of the application
Figma Design: Car Platform Design

