| Feature              | Description                          |
| -------------------- | ------------------------------------ |
| **Login Page**       | Users can log in via Email or Google |
| **User Dashboard**   | View cars and book                   |
| **Admin Dashboard**  | View all cars and delete             |
| **Add Car Form**     | Upload car info with image           |
| **Firebase Auth**    | Used for login                       |
| **Firestore DB**     | Stores car data and bookings         |
| **Firebase Storage** | Stores images                        |
| **React Router**     | Handles routing                      |
| **Tailwind CSS**     | Clean responsive UI                  |

